wikipedia_page.main: Charles Basil Royson Duffell (born 20 October 1986) is an English cricketer: a right-handed batsman and wicket-keeper who has played first-class cricket.

response: Duffell married Ann Murray Woodd, daughter of Colonel Basil Bethune Neville Woodd, of a landed gentry family of Shynewood, Shropshire; they have a son, the cricketer Charlie Duffell, and daughter, Rachel.Burke's Landed Gentry, 18th edition, vol.
